{"product_id":"cocoa-flow","title":"COCOA FLOW","description":"\u003cp\u003e MODEL HEIGHT 5'10 AND WAIST SIZE 32 WEARING M BOTTOMS.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e 420 GSM COTTON FLEECE\u003cbr\u003e COMBED \u0026amp; BIO-WASHED FINISH\u003cbr\u003e COFFEE BROWN WITH EMBROIDERY PRINT ON FRONT\u003cbr\u003e BAGGY FIT\u003cbr\u003e BELT LOOP FOR KEYS OR LIGHTER\u003cbr\u003e UNISEX ARTICLE [REFER TO SIZE CHART FOR ACCURATE MEASUREMENTS]. \u003c\/p\u003e \u003cul\u003e \u003cli\u003eCrafted from 420 GSM premium cotton fleece for superior comfort, structure, and durability.\u003c\/li\u003e \u003cli\u003eClean YRM embroidery print on the front adds refined streetwear aesthetics.\u003c\/li\u003e \u003cli\u003eSmall ankle zipper allows flexible styling and a sleek silhouette over sneakers.\u003c\/li\u003e \u003cli\u003eFunctional belt loop enhances practicality — ideal for holding keys, a lighter, or small essentials.\u003c\/li\u003e \u003cli\u003eStraight baggy silhouette designed for relaxed comfort and versatile streetwear styling.\u003c\/li\u003e \u003cli\u003eHeavyweight fabric ensures longevity while maintaining softness and premium feel.\u003c\/li\u003e \u003cli\u003ePerfect blend of utility, craftsmanship, and elevated minimalism for everyday wear.\u003c\/li\u003e \u003c\/ul\u003e \u003ch4\u003eCare Guide\u003c\/h4\u003e \u003cul\u003e \u003cli\u003eMachine wash the sweatpants inside out with like colors.\u003c\/li\u003e \u003cli\u003eUse cold water to preserve fabric quality and embroidery integrity.\u003c\/li\u003e \u003cli\u003eTumble dry on low heat or air dry to prevent shrinkage.\u003c\/li\u003e \u003cli\u003eStore in a cool, dry place to maintain shape and finish.\u003c\/li\u003e \u003c\/ul\u003e \u003ch4\u003eCore Features\u003c\/h4\u003e \u003cul\u003e \u003cli\u003eSweatpants constructed with 420 GSM fabric for a durable and substantial feel.\u003c\/li\u003e \u003cli\u003eStraight baggy fit for comfortable, versatile wear.\u003c\/li\u003e \u003cli\u003eUnisex article suitable for a wide range of body types and style preferences.\u003c\/li\u003e \u003cli\u003eBack pocket for convenient storage.\u003c\/li\u003e \u003cli\u003eElasticated waist for a custom fit and added style.\u003c\/li\u003e \u003cli\u003eSoft, breathable jersey backing ensures all-day comfort and airflow.\u003c\/li\u003e \u003c\/ul\u003e","brand":"DRIP STUDIOS","offers":[{"title":"S","offer_id":46885007229082,"sku":"Reign4(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)","price":2199.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":false},{"title":"M","offer_id":46885007261850,"sku":"Reign4(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)","price":2199.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":false},{"title":"L","offer_id":46885007294618,"sku":"Reign4(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)","price":2199.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":false},{"title":"XS","offer_id":46885007327386,"sku":"Reign4(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)","price":2199.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":false},{"title":"XL","offer_id":46885007360154,"sku":"Reign4(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)","price":2199.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":false},{"title":"XXL","offer_id":46885007392922,"sku":"Reign4(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)","price":2199.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":false}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0717\/2584\/2586\/files\/B94723ED-4940-4E13-B05B-46D5811F4CC8.png?v=1769957642","url":"https:\/\/dripdrip.in\/products\/cocoa-flow","provider":"DRIP STUDIOS","version":"1.0","type":"link"}